Each user can also check the status of three other users.
If a potential risk is detected, the app not only recommends self-quarantine, but also informs local health officials.Research analytics on mobile phone data, facial recognition technology, mobile phone tracking, and artificial intelligence are used to track infected people and people who came into contact with them in South Korea, Taiwan, and Singapore.
